::Kluster::

Kluster looks over at Phobia, his eyes a bit sad. "Unfortunately, the 
predacon intelligence got word of us launching off. They attacked and 
boarded. My tactical and science officers all died in the battle. As for the 
other leaders, they're currently at the Ark, fighting. I had to stay to 
welcome you here."

He looks around the conference room, "Would you like quarters untill the 
battle is over?"

(All the quarters in The Cybertronian Fire have the potential to be fully 
monitored, so it wouldn't really matter if they trusted him or not.)
